<section id="postChecks">
  <title><indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>payments</primary>

      <secondary>posting multiple</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>accounts payable</primary>

      <secondary>posting payments for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Post Payments</title>

  <para>To post multiple payments, go to <guimenuitem>Accounts &gt; Accounts
  Payable &gt; Payments &gt; Post Payments</guimenuitem>. The following screen
  will appear:</para>

  <para><screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/postChecks.png"/>
        </imageobject>

        <caption>Post Payments</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot></para>

  <para>When posting multiple payments, you are presented with the following
  options:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Bank Account</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Specify the bank account for the multiple payments you want to
        post.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Number of Unposted Payments</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Displays the total number of unposted payments.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term><indexterm significance="normal">
          <primary>payments</primary>

          <secondary>printing journal</secondary>
        </indexterm><indexterm significance="normal">
          <primary>payment journal</primary>

          <secondary>printing of</secondary>
        </indexterm>Print Payment Journal</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Select to print the payment journal.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>
</section>
